{
  "video_id": "GGScU5ESei4",
  "title": "Richard Sears: Planning for the end of oil",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18260.0,
      "text": "For the next few minutes we&#39;re going to talk about energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going to be a bit of a varied talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll try to spin a story about energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "and oil&#39;s a convenient starting place."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "The talk will be broadly about energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "but oil&#39;s a good place to start."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "And one of the reasons is this is remarkable stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "You take about eight or so carbon atoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "about 20 hydrogen atoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "you put them together in exactly the right way"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "and you get this marvelous liquid:"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "very energy-dense and very easy to refine"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "into a number of very useful products and fuels."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s great stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "Now, as far as it goes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a lot of oil out there in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s my little pocket map"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "of where it&#39;s all located."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "A bigger one for you to look at."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "But this is it, this is the oil in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "Geologists have a pretty good idea of where the oil is."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "This is about 100 trillion gallons"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "of crude oil"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "still to be developed and produced in the world today."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "Now, that&#39;s just one story about oil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "and we could end it there and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "\"Well, oil&#39;s going to last forever"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "because, well, there&#39;s just a lot of it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s actually more to the story than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "Oh, by the way, if you think you&#39;re very far from some of this oil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "1000 meters below where you&#39;re all sitting"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "is one of the largest producing oil fields in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "Come talk to me about it, I&#39;ll fill in some of the details if you want."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "So, that&#39;s one of the stories of oil; there&#39;s just a lot of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "But what about oil? Where is it in the energy system?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a little snapshot of 150 years of oil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s been a dominant part of our energy system"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "for most of those 150 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "Now, here&#39;s another little secret I&#39;m going to tell you about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "For the last 25 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "oil has been playing less and less of a role"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "in global energy systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "There was one kind of peak oil in 1985,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "when oil represented 50 percent of global energy supply."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s about 35 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been declining"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "and I believe it will continue to decline."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "Gasoline consumption in the U.S. probably peaked in 2007"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "and is declining."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "So oil is playing a less significant role"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "And so, 25 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "there was a peak oil;"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "just like, in the 1920s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "there was a peak coal;"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "and a hundred years before that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "there was a peak wood."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "This is a very important picture of the evolution of energy systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s been taking up the slack in the last few decades?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "Well, a lot of natural gas"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "and a little bit of nuclear, for starters."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "And what goes on in the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "Well, I think out ahead of us a few decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "is peak gas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "and beyond that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "peak renewables."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;ll tell you another little, very important"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "story about this picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m not pretending that energy use in total"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t increasing, it is --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s another part of the story. Come talk to me about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll fill in some of the details --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s a very important message here:"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "This is 200 years of history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "and for 200 years we&#39;ve been systematically decarbonizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "our energy system."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "Energy systems of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "becoming progressively -- year on year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "decade on decade, century on century --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "becoming less carbon intense."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "And that continues into the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "with the renewables that we&#39;re developing today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "reaching maybe 30 percent of primary energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "by mid century."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "Now that might be the end of the story --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "Okay, we just replace it all with conventional renewables --"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "but I think, actually, there&#39;s more to the story than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "And to tell the next part of the story --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "and this is looking out say 2100 and beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "What is the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "of truly sustainable, carbon-free energy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "Well, we have to take a little excursion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll start in central Texas."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a piece of limestone."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "I picked it up outside of Marble Falls, Texas."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about 400 million years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s just limestone, nothing really special about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "Now, here&#39;s a piece of chalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "I picked this up at MIT. It&#39;s a little younger."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s different than this limestone, you can see that."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "You wouldn&#39;t build a building out of this stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "and you wouldn&#39;t try to give a lecture and write on the chalkboard with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "Yeah, it&#39;s very different -- no, it&#39;s not different."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not different, it&#39;s the same stuff:"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "calcium carbonate, calcium carbonate."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s different is how the molecules are put together."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 263260.0,
      "text": "Now, if you think that&#39;s kind of neat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 263260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "the story gets really neat right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "Off the coast of California comes this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an abalone shell."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "Now, millions of abalone every year"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "make this shell."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "Oh, by the way, just in case you weren&#39;t already guessing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s calcium carbonate."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the same stuff as this"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "and the same stuff as this."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not the same stuff; it&#39;s different."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s thousands of times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "maybe 3,000 times tougher than this."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "And why? Because the lowly abalone"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "is able to lay down"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "the calcium carbonate crystals in layers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "making this beautiful, iridescent"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "mother of pearl."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "Very specialized material"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "that the abalone self-assembles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "millions of abalone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "all the time, every day, every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "This is pretty incredible stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "All the same, what&#39;s different?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "How the molecules are put together."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "Now, what does this have to do with energy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a piece of coal."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll suggest that this coal"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 322260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "is about as exciting"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "as this chalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "Now, whether we&#39;re talking about fuels"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "or energy carriers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "or perhaps novel materials for batteries"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "or fuel cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "nature hasn&#39;t ever built those perfect materials yet"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "because nature didn&#39;t need to."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "Nature didn&#39;t need to because, unlike the abalone shell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "the survival of a species didn&#39;t depend"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "on building those materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "until maybe now when it might just matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "So, when we think about the future of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "what would it be like"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "if instead of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "we could build the energy equivalent of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 365260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "just by rearranging the molecules differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "And so that is my story."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "The oil will never run out."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not because we have a lot of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not because we&#39;re going to build a bajillion windmills."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 381260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because, well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 381260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "thousands of years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "people invented ideas --"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "they had ideas, innovations, technology --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "and the Stone Age ended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "not because we ran out of stones."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s ideas, it&#39;s innovation, it&#39;s technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "that will end the age of oil, long before we run out of oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}